# 📲 OTP Authentication Rule

OTP login is implemented via SMS (pamenary/laravel-sms) and custom `OtpService`.

## 📁 Related Files
- @app/Services/OtpService.php
- @app/Http/Controllers/Auth/OtpLoginController.php
- @app/Http/Livewire/Auth/OtpLogin.php
- @database/migrations/create_otp_codes_table.php

## 🔐 Flow
- User enters mobile number
- OTP generated (6 digit, expires in 5 min)
- Code sent via `SmsChannel`
- User verifies, gets logged in or auto-created

## 💡 Notes
- Use rate limiting or block repeated OTP requests
- Configurable expiry via `config/otp.php`
- OTP code invalidated after use

✅ Livewire-based OTP login UI  
✅ Code tested with mocks 